    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"休假 reflects the importance of work-life balance in modern Chinese society. While traditional\nChinese culture emphasized continuous work, contemporary attitudes recognize the value of rest and\nrejuvenation. Taking 休假 is seen as necessary for maintaining productivity and personal well-being."}],"type":"paragraph"}
